<i>I want to be
the wandering sailor</i>


1038
00:50:12.160 --> 00:50:17.530
<i>We're silhouettes
by the light of the moon</i>


1039
00:50:19.760 --> 00:50:24.288
<i>I sit playing solitaire
by the window</i>


1040
